sentences.english: Compensation method was used to eliminate disturbance of coexisting element titanium.

sentences.english: In the Empire, a standard Dreadnaught carried a squadron of TIE fighters.

sentences.english: Microporous Si-Ti pillared montmorillonite materials were prepared in this paper.

sentences.english: Therefore, it is feasible to directly electrolytic produce low-titanium aluminium alloys in practice.

sentences.english: The only reason that a dog would have any titanium would be medical, he pointed out.

sentences.english: This review deals with the development in non cyclopentadienyl organic titanium complexes.

sentences.english: The effect of tiny amount of Titamium on the notch toughness of low carbon boron steel was investigated.

sentences.english: The mechanism of the effect of titanium on structure and properties of gray iron was proposed.

sentences.english: I could make it out of titanium if I wanted.

sentences.english: Immediate reconstruction with titanium plate for mandibular defect tumour-surgery;
